citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 12:40 pm on 25
September 2024. The inspector contacted the licensee by telephone. Failure to provide access to the facility, animals,
and records for inspection is a serious violation of the AWA and regulations. Failure to comply may result in enforcement
action.
End Section
